	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Fama de pace in <placeName ref="l832">Gallia</placeName> et quidem bona facta confirmatur magis et magis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Hac septimana ea de re scribunt syndici et senatus <placeName ref="l167">Genevensis</placeName> ad amplissimum senatum <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinum</placeName>, hodie mittunt cursorem et <placeName ref="l41">Bernenses</placeName> idipsum nunciantem; undecima ante meridiem scribunt idem amici ex <placeName ref="l18">Augusta Vindelicorum</placeName>, affirmant se hoc ipsum habere per postam ex <placeName ref="l15">Antverpia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Si itaque pax est facta, quod fere incipio credere, perpetuae agendae sunt gratiae deo, qui tot tam saevas et truculentas dissipavit practicas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Utinam deo nostro grati simus et vivamus vitam sanctam!</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Non memini eas me accepisse literas fortasse memoria laps s, de quibus tu scribis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Varia et multa simul nunciantur, de quibus, ubi habuero certiora, scribam, hoc est a feriis paschalibus, cum <placeName ref="l157">Francfordia</placeName> redierit <persName ref="p1227">Froschouerus</persName> noster amicorum oneratus literis ex <placeName>Palatinatu</placeName>, <placeName ref="l213">Hessia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l2562">Prussia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l830">Anglia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l2472">Polonia</placeName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Interim vale, charissime mi frater.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de"><foreign xml:lang="la">Dominus benedicat tibi,</foreign> das ir die passionwuchen wol ußrichtind und ein fröliche ostern habind!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tiguri</placeName> 9. aprilis 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Saluta d. d. d. consules<note type="margin">a.R.: cosss.</note>, <persName ref="p20473">Ganthnerum</persName>, <persName ref="p6130">Pontisellam</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Ocyssime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p495">Bullingerus</persName> tuissimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016">Thobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro fideli, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l98">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
